<taxonomicName authorityName="Shamshev &amp; Grootaert" authorityYear="2005" box="[537,733,316,342]" class="Insecta" family="Hybotidae" genus="Chersodromia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="43" pageNumber="44" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="singaporensis">
<emphasis box="[537,733,316,342]" italics="true" pageId="43" pageNumber="44">C. singaporensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName authority="Grootaert &amp; Shamshev, 2012" authorityName="Grootaert &amp; Shamshev" authorityYear="2012" box="[790,960,315,342]" class="Insecta" family="Hybotidae" genus="Chersodromia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="43" pageNumber="44" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="malaysiana" status="sp. nov.">
<emphasis box="[790,960,315,342]" italics="true" pageId="43" pageNumber="44">C. malaysiana</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[967,1058,316,342]" pageId="43" pageNumber="44" rank="species">sp. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
However, both these species have brownish palpi.
</paragraph>
